snippet.title: Vitamin Z - Launch Trailer | PS Vita
snippet.description:
Blow up zombie fruits and veggies, earning precious Z that you will use to upgrade your gear and delve deeper into the besieged lab.

http://www.vitamin-z-game.com
 
Zombies encroach on all sides. Dr. Rosa's plasma turret can’t move, so you must push zombies back before they overwhelm her! Earn Trophies, complete missions, and conquer the leaderboards! Vitamin Z is an action-packed free to play game that will have you on the edge of your seat!
